CustomField.description: Programmatically indicates whether a Maintenance Plan should generate the new batch (for Work Order Generation) upon completing the last work order in the previous batch. The value in this field will auto-populate a field of the same name on the Maintenance Plan.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Programmatically indicates whether a Maintenance Plan should generate the new batch (for Work Order Generation) upon completing the last work order in the previous batch. The value in this field will auto-populate a field of the same name on the Maintenance Plan.
CustomField.label: Generate New Batch Upon Completion
